node.text:
Excited to share my journey on motherhood, the fight for gender equality, and my dreams for a better future. Thank you @att for passing me the microphone and helping to amplify the voices of others through the She’s Connected series. ⁣
⁣
Together, we will build a better future for those who follow.⁣
#ATTAthlete
